Regions.Utter East:
{{Main|Utter East}}
The Utter East was a land made famous by tales of fancy that featured the legendary [[Five Kingdoms]] and their fantastic exploits. The kingdoms were formed by the [[Ffolk]] who had migrated from the [[Moonshae Isles]] and conquered the local people known as the [[Mar (ethnicity)|Mar]], and ruled over them for a number of decades.<ref name="GHotR-p93> While the Mar were able to reclaim their freedom, they remained stuck in an imbalance of power with the kingdoms of the Ffolk.<ref name="GHotR-p95 />

Among the Five Kingdoms were [[Doegan]], [[Edenvale]], [[Konigheim]], and the [[Free Cities of Parsanic]].
